{"title":"python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法","slug":"python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法","date":"2019-08-10T13:14:37.000Z","updated":"2021-04-04T05:20:00.204Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python3-进制转换及zfill函数和列表倒置的特殊方法.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"进制转换的问题：<br>主要用到的函数有：bin(),oct(),int(),hex()<br>","covers":null,"content":"<p>进制转换的问题：<br>主要用到的函数有：bin(),oct(),int(),hex()<br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h1 id=\"其他进制转成十进制：\"><a href=\"#其他进制转成十进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"其他进制转成十进制：\"></a>其他进制转成十进制：</h1><h1 id=\"二进制转成十进制：\"><a href=\"#二进制转成十进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二进制转成十进制：\"></a>二进制转成十进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(<span class=\"string\">'100'</span>,<span class=\"number\">2</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为二进制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"八进制转成十进制：\"><a href=\"#八进制转成十进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八进制转成十进制：\"></a>八进制转成十进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(<span class=\"string\">'04'</span>,<span class=\"number\">8</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为八进制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"十六进制转成十进制：\"><a href=\"#十六进制转成十进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十六进制转成十进制：\"></a>十六进制转成十进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">int(<span class=\"string\">'0x4'</span>,<span class=\"number\">16</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#注意输入的数值一定要是字符串的形式，第二个参数表示输入数值为十六进制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"十进制转成二进制：\"><a href=\"#十进制转成二进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十进制转成二进制：\"></a>十进制转成二进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bin(int(<span class=\"string\">'4'</span>,<span class=\"number\">10</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">bin(<span class=\"number\">4</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：0b100</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#0b表示二进制，如果想要截取，可以用[2:]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"十进制转成八进制：\"><a href=\"#十进制转成八进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十进制转成八进制：\"></a>十进制转成八进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">oct(int(<span class=\"string\">'4'</span>,<span class=\"number\">10</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">oct(<span class=\"number\">4</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：04</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#0表示八进制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"十进制转成十六进制：\"><a href=\"#十进制转成十六进制：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十进制转成十六进制：\"></a>十进制转成十六进制：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hex(int(<span class=\"string\">'4'</span>,<span class=\"number\">10</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hex(<span class=\"number\">4</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：0x4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#0x表示十六进制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"zfill函数：\"><a href=\"#zfill函数：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zfill函数：\"></a>zfill函数：</h1><p>str.zfill(width)<br>字符串扩展函数。width为扩展的宽度,扩张之后字符串右对齐，左侧填充0,和rjust(width,’0’)相似<br><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"123\"</span>.zfill(<span class=\"number\">5</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：00123        </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"123\"</span>.rjust(<span class=\"number\">5</span>,<span class=\"string\">'2'</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：22123  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"123\"</span>.ljust(<span class=\"number\">5</span>,<span class=\"string\">'2'</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#结果为：12322</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h1 id=\"列表逆置特殊方法：\"><a href=\"#列表逆置特殊方法：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"列表逆置特殊方法：\"></a>列表逆置特殊方法：</h1><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">list=[<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"number\">2</span>,<span class=\"number\">3</span>,<span class=\"number\">4</span>,<span class=\"number\">5</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(list[::<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#输出[5,4,3,2,1],表示所有列表元素逆置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(list[<span class=\"number\">4</span>:<span class=\"number\">2</span>:<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#输出[5,4],表示从下标为4到2(不包括2)的元素逆置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[],"tags":[]}